st you an excessive amount of money. It must provide shipping in a timely manner and have the ability to ship the type of materials and equipment you wish to send. Strong customer service is also vital as problems do occur with shipments and you need to know help is available when needed.","Here are the criteria we used to evaluate these shipping companies.","<strong>Shipping Options</strong><br/>When looking for the best shipping providers, you want a company that offers the right services to ensure your shipments arrive in a timely manner. Look for companies that offer express and priority delivery options if you need your shipment to arrive at its destination quickly. However, be aware that many companies charge an additional fee for any type of priority shipping. In fact, some companies may charge you double the cost of standard shipping.","Furthermore, some shipping solutions do not offer international options or are restrict it to Mexico and Canada. Other companies may only ship to certain areas within the United States.","<strong>Item Types</strong><br/>Several shipping services limit the type of items they will ship. Some companies will ship anything from a tiny parcel to a live animal. Many hazardous or dangerous goods have shipping restrictions. Most companies provide detailed lists of what can or cannot be shipped using their services.","Additionally, size is a key factor in the type of items a company will ship. Many companies have restrictions on the size and weight of a shipment. Most packages cannot be more than 130 inches long. This would limit many furniture items or large pieces of equipment.","<strong>Shipping Features</strong><br/>Losing a shipment or receiving a shipment that is damaged or destroyed can be a frustrating and overwhelming ordeal. Look for companies that provide tracking capabilities to help you follow a shipment. Insurance and protection options for high-value packages ensure that the items are received in excellent condition. Furthermore, many companies make it possible to prepare and pay for a shipment right from your computer.","<strong>Help &amp; Support</strong><br/>Customer support is crucial if you have questions or concerns regarding a shipment, or if you ve discovered a shipment is lost or stolen. Email, telephone and live chat are popular options that many shipping companies offer. Many solutions have numerous resources available on their website, such as forms, rate calculators and videos.","With a combination of the best features and services, you can find a quality shipping provider that will work hard to ensure your packages arrive on time and do not cost you a fortune to send."]},"id":"58ecbccf-61f7-4795-9c60-cb9632990447","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"7dcea76d-e41e-4839-a013-f6bcd1e332a4","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.ups.com/content/us/en/index.jsx?WT.svl=BrndMrk\">UPS</a>","<a href=\"http://www.tkqlhce.com/click-7658914-11368463\">FedEx</a>","<a href=\"https://www.usps.com\">United States Postal Service</a>","<a href=\"http://www.dhl-usa.com/en.html\">DHL</a>","<a href=\"http://yrc.com\">YRC Freight</a>","<a href=\"http://www.tnt.com/express/en_us/site/home.html\">TNT Express</a>","<a href=\"http://www.bolt-express.com\">Bolt Express</a>","<a href=\"http://www.ontrac.com/shippingservices.asp\">OnTrac</a>","<a href=\"http://www.tsscorp.us\">Top Shipping Systems</a>","<a href=\"http://www.transitsystems.com/ppc_shipping_services/?cpao=111&amp;cpca=Shipping+Only&amp;cpag=Shipping+Only&amp;kw=shipping+PHRASE&amp;gclid=Cj0KEQjwjtGfBRCN4-LU9ODG1-wBEiQAy_Xp7yCLouITHu2W242-wPsDAitpuef6_ctwwF3lIBYya4EaAlNs8P8HAQ\">Transit Systems</a>"],"type":"ul"},"id":"89cbdac4-20ad-44fd-ad58-2504a466a7c5","type":"list"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"comparison_page_1250","url":"/best-shipping-companies","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jill-bowers","url":"/author/jill-bowers","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Jill Bowers","dateMod